description:
Putt your own stylish spin on the game as you tee off with one of 3 new hats or floaties with the Caddy Pack!

The Caddy Pack comes with:
•Rowboat floatie
•Teacup floatie
•Goose floatie
•Triceratops hat
•‘Beanie’ propeller hat 
•Australian ‘slouch’ hat (outback style hat)
name: Golf With Your Friends - Caddy Pack
